{
  "title": "ISic001674. Opus signinum pavement inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Χαῖρε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Χαῖρε</span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"πίει\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">[πί]ε̣ι̣</span>  <span data-text=\"εὖ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[εὖ]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἱλαρὸς\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ἱλαρὸς</span>  <span data-text=\"εἶ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">εἶ</span>  <span data-text=\"νυ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">νυ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Χαῖρε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"πίει\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">[..]..</span><span data-text=\"εὖ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[..]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἱλαρὸς\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ΙΛΑΡΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"εἶ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΙ</span><span data-text=\"νυ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ΝΥ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001674_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\" src=\"ISic001674_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001674.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\" src=\"ISic001674-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001674_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001674_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001674.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001674-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Isler 1986</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 2\">line.2: <span>Isler 1985: ΙΛΑΡΟΣ Ι ΝΥ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 35.1002 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 36.0836 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 1988.0245 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a>  </li><li> 1993.0714 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a>  </li><li> Isler 1985 13-15 with fig. 20 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002220\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002220</a>  </li><li> Isler 1986 72-73 with abb. 3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002487\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002487</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Tsakirgis 1990 441 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002486\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002486</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Deeply engraved letters of slightly varying height (omicron/theta small and midline, iota extended beyond other letters). Letters have pronounced circular terminations to many strokes (punched). Alpha has straight bar; epsilon has short middle stroke; theta is small and midline with central point; iota is tall; pi has verticals of equal length; rho appears open; sigma has diverging upper and lower strokes.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-tyoe3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ tyoe3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ type3</a> </p> Lines 1-2  80  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
